Subject: Re: [ckrm-tech] [PATCH 0/2] resource control file system - aka	containers on top of nsproxy!
Sender: linux-kernel-owner@vger.kernel.org
Precedence: bulk
List-ID: <linux-kernel.vger.kernel.org>
